content:
No need to apologize! I'm here to help and provide information. Thank you for clarifying that Dr. Maria Rodriguez is a fictional character.

Yes, please do suggest some books, articles, and online resources on feminist art in the 1970s. I'm interested in learning more about this topic and would appreciate your recommendations.

Additionally, if you have any resources on feminist art in general, including its history, key figures, and notable movements, I'd love to explore those as well.

Thank you for your help and guidance!
